### F

*   [Fibonacci Quarterly](/Fibonacci_Quarterly) – Dedicated to the study of the Fibonacci sequence and related topics. A bit of a specialty, but fascinating.
*   [Forum of Mathematics, Pi](/Forum_of_Mathematics,_Pi) – A newer open-access journal publishing high-quality mathematical research.
*   [Forum of Mathematics, Sigma](/Forum_of_Mathematics,_Sigma) – Another open-access journal from the same publisher, likely covering similar ground.
*   [Fractals](/Fractals_(journal)) – The mathematics of fractals and chaos. Visually appealing and mathematically complex.
