*   [Gentleman's Diary](/Gentleman%27s_Diary) – Sounds like an antiquated publication, possibly containing mathematical puzzles or early scientific notes.
*   [Geombinatorics](/Geombinatorics) – A journal that blends geometry and combinatorics.
