*   [Hiroshima Mathematical Journal](/Hiroshima_Mathematical_Journal) – A Japanese journal of mathematics.
*   [Historia Mathematica](/Historia_Mathematica) – The journal for the history of mathematics. Understanding the past is crucial for appreciating the present.
*   [Homology, Homotopy and Applications](/Homology,_Homotopy_and_Applications) – Focuses on algebraic topology and its applications.

